==English==

===Noun===
'''pony'''

# Any of several small breeds of [[horse]] under 14.2 [[hands]].
# A small serving of an alcoholic beverage.
# A measure of one [[ounce]] of liquor.
# (''Australia'') A serving of 140 milliliters of beer.

